     - Remove dependency management stuff, that is for parent POMs to easily set the versions of children dependencies
     - Set up build lifecyle to "build->unit_test->integration_test"
     - Set up environments, DEV and PROD. Can we optionally disable security in DEV to avoid having to log in to anything?
